reviewText: Loved them all keep them all coming and have a happy and wonderful but safe New Year.
This was a complete interview with selena Gomez. Super boring. They should have added some of her childhood memories with pictures and at least one or more of her music videos..
my daughter is a huge fan. however she was expecting to see some songs. there were no songs only interviews. very disappointed.

I was disappointed with this dvd.  I was expecting more of a biography, but it was really just an hour's worth of 3 or so different interviews with Selena.  This really wasn't worth $10.00
